<article>
<h1 class='text-right m-4'>the hell is LoNK???</h1>
<div>
<p>glad you asked! </p>
LoNK stands for <img alt='Losers of Near-Kyiv' src="{{'/'|url}}imgs/logo.png" class='hover:rotate-4 ease-in-out transition-all duration-1100 hover:scale-115 h-[5em] inline'>, of course!
</div>

<div class='text-center p-2'>
and it is an <strong class='underline decoration-3 decoration-dashed decoration-[#a50505]'>ANIMATED WEBSERIES</strong> CONCEPT, currently existing as a multimedia project - primarly a <strong>WEBCOMIC</strong>.
<br>
<div class='flex md:flex-row flex-col'>
<img src='/imgs/example.png' alt="" class='hover:scale-105 ease-in-out transition-all duration-900 border-3 border-red-700 border-dashed -rotate-2 m-2 md:w-[30%]'>
<div class='md:w-[70%] flex-center'>
<p>
the story follows <b>FOUR ROOMMATES:</b> <b class='text-dima'>DIMA</b>, <b class='text-acryl'>ACRYL</b>, <b class='text-zaria'>LUCHEZAR</b> and <b class='text-misha'>MIKHEI</b>, who all happen to be students in a fictional, slightly more fantasy, no-war version of <a target='_blank' href='https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kyiv_Oblast'>NEAR-KYIV, UKRAINE</a>.
<br><br>
they hang out. they cook food. they fight over the laundry. they hate each other. they hang out again! ⭐❤️
<br><br>
if you are interested in a <b>SLICE OF LIFE</b> story with diverse, charming characters and silly internet humour, you're in the right place!<br>
</p>
</div>

</div>
</article>

